sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant B as Broker

    Note over C,B: TCP接続確立後

    C->>B: CONNECT
    Note right of C: protocol="MQTT"<br/>level=4 (v3.1.1)<br/>clean_session=true<br/>keep_alive=60<br/>client_id="zig-client"

    alt プロトコルレベル確認
        B->>B: protocol_level == 4 ?
    end

    alt 接続承認
        B->>C: CONNACK
        Note left of B: session_present=false<br/>return_code=0 (accepted)
        Note over C,B: 接続成功 -- Pub/Sub 可能
    else 接続拒否 (例: 認証エラー)
        B->>C: CONNACK
        Note left of B: session_present=false<br/>return_code=4 (bad_credentials)
        B--xC: TCP接続を切断
    end

    Note over C,B: Keep Alive による生存確認

    loop Keep Alive 間隔ごと
        C->>B: PINGREQ
        B->>C: PINGRESP
    end

    Note over C,B: 切断

    C->>B: DISCONNECT
    C--xB: TCP接続を閉じる
